":"Jean-Paul Hurier","popularity":0.5768,"profile_path":"/rW6tB0seNtgV5Gf37Z6rmTbuL8K.jpg","credit_id":"678e8cac859fb4e6a86e3712","department":"Sound","job":"Sound Re-Recording Mixer"},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":81053,"known_for_department":"Crew","name":"Emmanuel Lanzi","original_name":"Manu Lanzi","popularity":1.2122,"profile_path":"/5oJtCgm3YswkFEaULGH4UZnOSvY.jpg","credit_id":"678e8d0c68e0d873636e3692","department":"Crew","job":"Stunt Coordinator"},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1539072,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Sophie le Breton","original_name":"Sophie le Breton","popularity":0.1853,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"678e8dc568e0d873636e36ff","department":"Directing","job":"Script Supervisor"}]}},"person_71491_translations":{"at":1774211379163,"data":{"id":71491,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Patrick Descamps, né le 13 décembre 1956 à Mons, est un comédien, metteur en scène et professeur de théâtre belge.\n\nAprès avoir décroché un premier prix de déclamation et de phonétique au Conservatoire de Mons, Patrick Descamps devient professeur de déclamation à l'Académie de Colfontaine (1977-1979). Dès 1988, il est directeur de production et joue au Kollectif Théâtre, puis il préside les \"États Généraux d'un Jeune Théâtre\" (1994-1999), est chargé de Cours au Conservatoire royal de Mons (1996-2005), et prend les fonctions de directeur artistique du théâtre de l'Ancre à Charleroi (2002-2007).\n\nSur scène, il est l’interprète de plusieurs pièces du répertoire classique, telles que: Britannicus de Racine, Le Misanthrope de Molière, Kean d'après Alexandre Dumas ou La Nuit des rois et Roméo et Juliette de Shakespeare, mais aussi de nombreuses œuvres d’auteurs contemporains comme La Cerisaie de Tchekhov, La Danse de mort d'August Strindberg, Qui a peur de Virginia Woolf ? d'Edward Albee ou Garde à vue d'après John Wainwright, sur des dialogues de Michel Audiard.\n\nEn 1985, il reçoit l’Ève du meilleur comédien pour son interprétation de Mephisto dans Un Faust de Jean Louvet et pour le rôle d'Answald dans La Trilogie du revoir de Botho Strauss. En 1996, il décroche le Prix Tenue de ville du meilleur comédien pour Jasha de Yasmina Reza.\n\nEn 1981, il signe sa première mise en scène au Théâtre de l'Ancre, plusieurs autres suivront, parmi lesquelles Chambres de Philippe Minyana et L'Indicible de Jean-Marie Piemme.\n\nIl aborde le cinéma, en 2002, dans Après la vie et Cavale deux films signés Lucas Belvaux. Acteur de composition, il a apparaît, entre autres, dans Itinéraires de Christophe Otzenberger, Nue Propriété de Joachim Lafosse, À l'origine de Xavier Giannoli, Mineurs 27 de Tristan Aurouet et La French de Cédric Jimenez. Son rôle dans Versailles de Pierre Schöller lui permet de remporter un double prix d’interprétation au Festival Jean Carmet de Moulins.\n\nPour la télévision, il joue des rôles récurrents dans les séries La Commune et Un village français.\n\nSource: Article \"Patrick Descamps\" de Wikipédia en français, soumis à la licence CC-BY-SA.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Patrick Descamps","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Patrick Descamps","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"派屈克·德康普斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"帕特里克·德康","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Патрик Декамп","primary":false}}]}},"person_1346848_translations":{"at":1774211403520,"data":{"id":1346848,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Yeon Woo-jin (born Kim Bong-hoe on July 5, 1984) is a South Korean actor. He started in the entertainment industry as a model and gained recognition as an actor with his role in Arang and the Magistrate (2012) which earned him nomination for Best New Actor. He expands his acting repertoire on leading roles in Marriage, Not Dating (2014), Divorce Lawyer in Love (2015), Introverted Boss (2017), Queen for Seven Days (2017) and Judge vs. Judge (2017).","name":"Yeon Woo-jin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（1984年7月5日出生于金奉昊）是韩国演员。他以模特的身份进入娱乐圈，并凭借在《阿朗与裁判官》（2012 年）中的角色获得了演员的认可，这为他赢得了最佳新演员的提名。他在《婚姻，不约会》（2014 年）、《恋爱中的离婚律师》（2015 年）、《内向的老板》（2017 年）、《七日女王》（2017 年）和《法官对法官》（2017 年）中扩大了自己的表演曲目。","name":"延宇振","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"연우진","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"延玗臻","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PT","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kim Bong-hoe","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yeon Woo-jin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Ο Γεόν Γου-τζιν (Yeon Woo-jin) είναι ένας Νοτιοκορεάτης ηθοποιός. Ξεκίνησε στη βιομηχανία του θεάματος ως μοντέλο και κέρδισε την αναγνώριση ως ηθοποιός με τον ρόλο του στο Arang and the Magistrate (2012) που του χάρισε μια υποψηφιότητα για τον καλύτερο νέο ηθοποιό. Επέκτεινε το υποκριτικό ρεπερτόριό του σε πρωταγωνιστικούς ρόλους στις ταινίες Marriage, Not Dating (2014), Divorce Lawyer in Love (2015), Introverted Boss (2017), Queen for Seven Days (2017) και Judge vs Judge (2017).","name":"Γεόν Γου-τζιν","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ён У Чжин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（1984 年 7 月 5 日出生於金奉昊）是韓國演員。他以模特的身份進入娛樂圈，並憑藉在《阿朗與裁判官》（2012 年）中的角色獲得了演員的認可，這為他贏得了最佳新演員的提名。他在《婚姻，不約會》（2014 年）、《戀愛中的離婚律師》（2015 年）、《內向的老闆》（2017 年）、《七日女王》（2017 年）和《法官對法官》（2017 年）中擴大了自己的表演曲目。","name":"延宇振","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ヨン・ウジン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yeon Woo-jin","primary":false}}]}},"person_583446_translations":{"at":1774211405377,"data":{"id":583446,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Hermila Roberta Pires Guedes (Cabrobó, November 27, 1980), better known as Hermila Guedes, is a Brazilian actress. She is one of the most awarded actresses in Brazilian cinema.","name":"Hermila Guedes","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Hermila Guedes é uma atriz brasileira.\n\nNascida em Cabrobó, Pernambuco, Hermila mudou-se com a irmã Hermana (mais nova) para Olinda aos 10 anos, depois que o pai, policial, foi assassinado. Depois, mudaram-se para Recife, aonde ia desde muito cedo para tratamento de sua vitiligo. Em Recife, cursou a faculdade de Turismo e, depois, de Letras, na UFPE.\n\nHermila foi casada com o ator Tatto Medini, com quem tem uma filha, Celina, nascida em 2008. Atualmente, é casada com o delegado Roberto Wanderley, com quem tem mais duas filhas, Stella e Helena.","name":"Hermila Guedes","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Эрмила Гуэдес","primary":false}}]}},"person_3718807_translations":{"at":1774211414056,"data":{"id":3718807,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Zhang Ruoyu is a female voice actress from China.","name":"Zhang Ruoyu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"张若瑜是中国内地的女性配音演员。","name":"张若瑜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ruoyu Zhang","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"張若瑜是中國內地的女性配音演員。","name":"張若瑜","primary":false}}]}}}}